---
title: Cheese and Chorizo Quesadillas with tomato salsa and cooling creme fraiche
description: These tortillas are a family favourite recipe that features lashings of melted cheese, slightly spiced chorizo and softened veg for a filling that's too good to pass up. Refreshment comes in the form of tomato salsa and zesty creme fraiche.
